node.text: Big thank you to @booricollections we love our new furniture for our baby girl! We cannot explain how easy it was to assemble! Not like other furniture that takes hours it’s mostly put together already! Also it has amazing soft closing doors to stop any accidents happening! The quality is also so strong we love them so much! Cannot recommend them enough! We do not like to promote much usually but honest we can say we are so amazed by these! Once again thank you so much @booricollections please go check them out. They deserve it!💙. Full baby room reveal coming soon to YouTube!!..💙. #gifted
